Subject: Hackforge Demo
Description: Windsor Hackforge is a shared space where creative technological minds come together and make things happen. They are bringing a hands-on project to this side of the Detroit River. Watching is free, but attendees who want to build along will be asked for a donation to cover the costs of materials.  Speakers include:Sarah Morris - Track: DIY, Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
